{"tid":2125521,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「反擊Brain cha」手機+平版一齊睇廣告","createTime":"2020-07-26T08:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T14:09:17.000Z","uid":128210,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"67f7bbd7cb4ceb9360bbfdcc2b1acd7334062d76","tid":2125521,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T08:43:39.000Z","msg":"係咁既，雖然呀查生（個姓亂打，wfc佢姓咩）一直有係YouTube 擺大量廣告。<br />\n但正如佢所講，佢有交廣告費就有資格擺廣告。<br />\n<br />\n不過咁，google落廣告一直都係計睇片率+點擊黎計收費，所以我一般睇到好唔鍾意既廣告就睇晒佢，等佢廣告費貴啲。<br />\n到昨晚，睇咗bain 段回應k先生既回應，太串，條撚樣實在太串，忍無可忍。<br />\n我決定開始仰慕呀歪生，佢實在太聰明。<br />\n要仰慕佢，就梗係要睇佢既廣告片啦：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TC9HemO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTC9HemO.jpg&h=e40a8082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先係google 不斷search 佢個名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9x2eng.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9x2eng.jpg&h=ef810437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後去睇條咁撚多廣告既片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NhQ7HN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NhQ7HN.jpg&h=534962a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就可以睇佢嘅廣告片了，好滾動。<br />\n我睇完會按條片咖，可以知多啲好厲害既教學呀<del>同廣告費會貴啲</del><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SKpoJgH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSKpoJgH.jpg&h=f81435c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有一堆電腦未搵充電線充電黎睇佢啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己呢，就去打下cs先<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/veBKsKD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FveBKsKD.jpg&h=9190fdf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然見到最仰慕既y先生嘅廣告係一定要按。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDXd5wF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDXd5wF.jpg&h=75fa4360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝Brain 生意<span class=\"x-small\">同<del>廣告</del>養YouTuber 費</span>蒸蒸日上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附上YouTube 收費方式<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50zsqBd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50zsqBd.jpg&h=6941452f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8508009b7e0a2877c893a2d6e3b07e446147a183","tid":2125521,"uid":258241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"要睇幾多次先收查生一蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c63930532ff8847d2bfc54dfa65bb4c2f8d18b5","tid":2125521,"uid":53368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8508009b7e0a2877c893a2d6e3b07e446147a183","tid":2125521,"uid":258241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"要睇幾多次先收查生一蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"其實youtube google ad好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac29dbab21bcceaecbccd71f9f40f153b8999da","tid":2125521,"uid":242605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T08:55:38.000Z","msg":"去google 狂search 「Brian Cha 呃人」"},{"pid":"e3023ea6b56943d7d2a4abd378a03df07d04b520","tid":2125521,"uid":184746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8508009b7e0a2877c893a2d6e3b07e446147a183","tid":2125521,"uid":258241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"要睇幾多次先收查生一蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:06:46.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"7365d248c20ec243e2200580ea2480b2bfc6e593","tid":2125521,"uid":31246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T09:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31925900580861645329773938bc5c7f04c59514","tid":2125521,"uid":356847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor